catDescription: Sessions to wake you up and stimulate you

programs.title: SMR (Sensory Motor Rythm) | 24 min | 14Hz
programs.subtitle: Used to achieve relaxed attention

programs.title: Beta 1 - Sharpen the mind | 20 min | 19Hz
programs.subtitle: A great way to get going in the morning without caffeine. This session helps reduce ADD and SAD symptoms. May cause anxiety.

programs.title: Beta 2 - Sharpen the mind | 20 min | 23H
programs.subtitle: Like Beta 1, but with a gigher target frequency range. May give a more energizing jor intense feeling.

programs.title: Mental flexibility | 22 min | Variable
programs.subtitle: To 'loosen up' a stuck mind. Can also be used for fibromyalgia.

catDescription: Sessions to relax and calm you

programs.title: 'Wise guy' Alpha | 30 min | 10.6Hz
programs.subtitle: It has been shown that people with fast running alpha waves have higher than average IQs.

programs.title: Coffee break Alpha | 15 min | 10Hz
programs.subtitle: UGreat for a little rest during your coffee or lunch break.

programs.title: Alpha Relaxer | 30 min | 12Hz
programs.subtitle: Healthy alpha is 10 Hz. Most disorders have alpha slowing. This session reestablishes the natural alpha rhythm. Good for beginners.

programs.title: Schumann Resonance | 22 min | 7.8Hz
programs.subtitle: For a quick, through afternoon meditation. Calms 'hyper/chattery' minds. For those on the go.

programs.title: Theta | 36 min | 5.5Hz
programs.subtitle: Use for creative visualization. May also be used for sleep.

catDescription: Sessions to help you focus and concentrate

programs.title: SMR for Reading | 20 min | 13Hz
programs.subtitle: Improve attention and alertness while reading.

programs.title: SMR/Beta | 24 min | 13.5Hz
programs.subtitle: A gentle and entraining session that helps to focus mental functioning and memory.

programs.title: Brain Booster | 30 min | 14Hz
programs.subtitle: Use to impove mental functioning and memory, Based on Budzynski's study. Similar to ADD and learning, but with gentler transitions. Useful for seniors and those with ADD.

programs.title: ADD and Learning | 26 min | 19Hz
programs.subtitle: This session has rapid transitions for mental stimulation to help keep the user 'engaged' in the session. Used in the ADD study published in the journal of Neurotherapy.

programs.title: Skill & Sports Development | 24 min | 18Hz
programs.subtitle: Use this session to develop any skill or improve performance. Visualize feeling your best during the first half(alpha). Then visualize your perfect performance during the second half(beta) of the session.

catDescription: Sessions to help you relax and fall asleep

programs.title: Schumann for Sleep | 40 min | 7.8Hz
programs.subtitle: For effective deep meditation and to improve the onset of sleep. Calms 'hyper/chattery' minds. Ideal for those with insomnia who have a busy mind and tense body.

programs.title: Meditate to Sleep | 45 min | 4Hz
programs.subtitle: A gentle and entraining session that helps to focus mental functioning and memory.

programs.title: Alpha/Theta for Sleep | 36 min | 10-6Hz
programs.subtitle: This session can really help to break up distressing thoughts that are interfering with sleep.

programs.title: SMR for Sleep | 40 min | 14Hz
programs.subtitle: This session has rapid transitions for mental stimulation to help keep the user 'engaged' in the session. Used in the ADD study published in the journal of Neurotherapy.

programs.title: >Delta | 45 min | 3.5Hz
programs.subtitle: To aid with falling asleep. Best for those with fibromyalgia.

catDescription: Sessions to help your mood and reduce stress

programs.title: Mood Booster 1 | 30 min | 8Hz
programs.subtitle: Settles down negative emotions from the right brain while stimulating the left brain to rebalance alpha asymmetry.

programs.title: Mood Booster 2 | 42 min | 8Hz
programs.subtitle: This session has an alpha front end to reduce anxiety and enhance relaxation.

programs.title: Sub-Delta | 24 min | 1Hz
programs.subtitle: Mildly dissociating. Calms the hypothalamus. Beneficial for some with fibromyalgia and hypertension.

programs.title: Extended Deep Alpha Relaxer | 80 min | 8.4Hz
programs.subtitle: Stay relaxed for your dental, massage, physiotherapy, chiropractic and other appointments.

programs.title: Paradise | 36 min | 6.5Hz
programs.subtitle: A gentle slide down to Theta. Extroverts with low anxiety produce high levels of this frequency.
